text: Monika Grzebinoga (born 1 March 1985) is a road cyclist from Poland. She represented her nation at the 2006, 2007, 2008 and 2009 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1985 births Category:Polish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
